rc=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-11.png?rev=2844304\" alt=\"QUickly switch between search views.\"></a><p>QUickly switch between search views.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-12.png?rev=2844304\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-12.png?rev=2844304\" alt=\"View your events on a Google Map, filter with searches.\"></a><p>View your events on a Google Map, filter with searches.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-13.png?rev=2844304\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-13.png?rev=2844304\" alt=\"Multiple calendar styles, fully responsive according to the width of the calendar.\"></a><p>Multiple calendar styles, fully responsive according to the width of the calendar.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-14.png?rev=2844304\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-14.png?rev=2844304\" alt=\"Responsivve way for mini-calendar to intuitively show dates with many events within a quick glance.\"></a><p>Responsivve way for mini-calendar to intuitively show dates with many events within a quick glance.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-15.png?rev=2844304\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-15.png?rev=2844304\" alt=\"Responsive lists that adapt to the size of its containing content.\"></a><p>Responsive lists that adapt to the size of its containing content.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-16.png?rev=2844304\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-16.png?rev=2844304\" alt=\"Clean forms for submitting and managing events, as well as booking events for users.\"></a><p>Clean forms for submitting and managing events, as well as booking events for users.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-17.png?rev=2844304\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-17.png?rev=2844304\" alt=\"Dashboard graph widget for quick review of your event bookings with tons of meaningful data views.\"></a><p>Dashboard graph widget for quick review of your event bookings with tons of meaningful data views.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-18.png?rev=2849641\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-18.png?rev=2849641\" alt=\"Grid view for displaying your upcoming events at a glance\"></a><p>Grid view for displaying your upcoming events at a glance</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:20630:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Highly Satisfied After Years of Use and Over 650 Events</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 van de 5 sterren\" data-title-template=\"%s van de 5 sterren\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Door <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/galponartes/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d2095a9edf7f0c377e653375fb0f4e8f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d2095a9edf7f0c377e653375fb0f4e8f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/galponartes/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">galponartes</a> op <span class=\"review-date\">augustus 6, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We\'ve been using the Events Manager plugin since 2017 with the free version, and since 2022 we\'ve upgraded to the Pro version. With over 650 events hosted at our theater since then, this plugin has been instrumental in managing our event reservations, building a mailing list of our audience, and maintaining smoother communication with them.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We\'re very pleased with the continuous development and new features that the Events Manager team keeps introducing. It\'s clear that they are dedicated to improving the plugin over time. We hope the project continues to grow, and we will remain grateful for the support and innovations they provide.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Please fix</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 van de 5 sterren\" data-title-template=\"%s van de 5 sterren\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Door <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thompsonaire/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6a6e646da0ec662d234af5e7ae25d15a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6a6e646da0ec662d234af5e7ae25d15a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thompsonaire/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">thompsonaire</a> op <span class=\"review-date\">augustus 6, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Below is a description of what happened to me.  Hopefully if it happens to you this may help fix.  I have not tried to update my app yet but I will be doing so shortly.  But first I must say this.  I have both a paid version and several free versions of this.  I did not know how to ask for support so I posted a review (since that was the first location I stumbled on where I could write something).  I get very lost in here with all the options..  Anyway,  Marcus (who I found out is one of the developers) has been AMAZING to me.  Even with my severe frustration trying to fix (What was a glitch in the app) he remained calm and has emailed me several tips and tricks that has helped me get things back on track.  With support like that he has definitely earned a 5 STAR review.  Maybe more!  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thank you SIR!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So I was updating all my sites and unwittingly selected update all. If you are using this plug in and have one of the earlier versions DO NOT UPDATE! It will mess up your site. Or more specifically it will mess up the calendar view. There are ways to fix it and if you are good at code or want to try to search for line 609 in the php file go for it. Not an option for me. I need to find some place I can get version Version 6.4.7.3.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I was asked to fix this review.  But the review is precisely what happened to me and a couple of my sites.  While I tried to find a way to fix it I do not know code and I also find it very difficult to navigate these forums.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>That being said.  I will give \"Marcus\" (a person who sent me an email with suggestions who I do not know who he is) credit.  He gave me a couple of ideas of what to do and I was able to find a plugin that allows me to \"Roll Back\" to a previous version.  That is what I did and that fixed how the display showed on the site.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now I have also recieved an email that says that the latest release should fix the problem.  I am unsure if I even want to try it.  Its like getting bitten by a dog and then being told \"You can pet him he is frendly\"...  Yea...  UM NO..  I will give them a higher star rating since they did reach out and try to help.  But for now I will just stay with my Version 6.4.7.3.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Dificil mais fácil</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 van de 5 sterren\" data-title-template=\"%s van de 5 sterren\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Door <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jbeltraojr/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bf6cc765f6500c66c53daf72631b32a7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bf6cc765f6500c66c53daf72631b32a7?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jbeltraojr/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">José Beltrão Júnior <small>(jbeltraojr)</small></a> op <span class=\"review-date\">augustus 5, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trabalhoso mais eficiente.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 van de 5 sterren\" data-title-template=\"%s van de 5 sterren\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Door <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/reneegoodog/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fae0e245bb582efce79c15d8c579a287?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fae0e245bb582efce79c15d8c579a287?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/reneegoodog/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">reneegoodog</a> op <span class=\"review-date\">augustus 5, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Plugins will always have glitches but it\'s how a business resolves those issues that matter. I\'m pleased to say that the EM team exceeded my expectations. There was an issue, they joined the dots that others were affected, then identified the issue, worked out a fix, and provided a plugin update to resolve in a timely manner. All done professionally and graciously. Thank you to the EM team!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great support and a Free plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 van de 5 sterren\" data-title-template=\"%s van de 5 sterren\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Door <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tanboxer/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c4c6cba9798143848668e05f6052e822?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c4c6cba9798143848668e05f6052e822?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tanboxer/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tanboxer</a> op <span class=\"review-date\">juli 27, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This was installed with one of my themes so it was only the free version I was using.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I need help and some questions regard possible future features and the responses were quick and most importantly helpful.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I would say if you use this properly it could handle any event scenarios you would have for your wordpress projects. I will be upgrading to pro as I feel confident I will be looked after and the plugin has much promise for the future.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>kind regards, Andrew</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great responsive support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 van de 5 sterren\" data-title-template=\"%s van de 5 sterren\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Door <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joannacraig/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0bc9834becb787982a0c80f682527a74?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0bc9834becb787982a0c80f682527a74?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joannacraig/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Joanna <small>(joannacraig)</small></a> op <span class=\"review-date\">juli 4, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Very speedy reply to an issue and clear explanation of solution. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Nice Event Manager</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 van de 5 sterren\" data-title-template=\"%s van de 5 sterren\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Door <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kaytellehoelgmailcom/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6cefbf4dbdb4ce0eb1506cf0391bd10f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6cefbf4dbdb4ce0eb1506cf0391bd10f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kaytellehoelgmailcom/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">kaytellehoel <small>(kaytellehoel@gmail.com)</small></a> op <span class=\"review-date\">juni 21, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nice Event Manager plugin but the support  is too slow.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Going downhill</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 van de 5 sterren\" data-title-template=\"%s van de 5 sterren\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Door <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/noctividus/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d3001ade83bc9adc5259de2cc7774293?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d3001ade83bc9adc5259de2cc7774293?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/noctividus/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">noctividus</a> op <span class=\"review-date\">juni 5, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This plugin has grown past the development capabilities of the people maintaining it. I have the pro version, and it\'s basically one guy with very basic troubleshooting skills. When a true bug is found, there\'s no resolution and worse yet, no timeframe for resolution.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A while ago, they did a major upgrade and changed their database structure. Reporting isn\'t backwards compatible across that database change. If you look at your database, you see what they\'re doing with tables- <br />wp_em_bookings_meta<br />wp_em_bookings_meta_copy<br />wp_em_bookings_meta_copy_2</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>They\'re using 16 tables in total to manage this plugin. Complete mess. Super sloppy. I\'m very invested in this plugin, but I\'m about to jump ship.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Decent Functionality, But Be Aware</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 van de 5 sterren\" data-title-template=\"%s van de 5 sterren\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Door <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/edwayt/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cec3a568eae2715ba2cbe42985e50015?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cec3a568eae2715ba2cbe42985e50015?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/edwayt/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">edwayt</a> op <span class=\"review-date\">mei 31, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This plugin has pretty good functionality for a very reasonable price.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>But BEWARE! The code, support, and communication are pretty poor, and the docs are hit and miss (and sometimes outdated when they are available).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">very poor support even in paid version</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 van de 5 sterren\" data-title-template=\"%s van de 5 sterren\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Door <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/steve098/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/79ce959acfe7c829608e77c6ef8e94b7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/79ce959acfe7c829608e77c6ef8e94b7?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/steve098/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">steve098</a> op <span class=\"review-date\">mei 6, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A potentially great system for managing events, but if something doesn\'t work then the support is basically non-existent.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Don\'t rely on this plugin for anything but a small website where you are able to manually take and fix bookings when you inevitably come across a bug that causes double-bookings/blocks people from booking/doesn\'t update online payment status/doesn\'t email customers (these are just a handful of the outstanding bugs currently on the support forum that have been \'with the devs\' to fix for MONTHS).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The support in the \'pro\' paid version consists of a private forum to post your problem to. It is full of people pleading over-and-over again for months to fix fundamental flaws and bugs, and the first line support technician just replying over-and-over that they have \'raised it again with the devs\'. In the meantime people\'s businesses are losing custom or having to refund customers because the booking system has done something wrong due to a bug.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The only real replies from the plugin authors are where the support technician answers basic functionality questions like \"how do I do x,y,z\", but if there is a bug (of which are many and frequent) then there is absolutely no chance of a speedy resolution or any comeback.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There is no support email address, no support telephone line, no SLA, no comeback if your site doesn\'t work because of a bug…and the limited documentation is out-of-date as well!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>But, if you just want something to manage events, present calendars, take bookings (with payments if you are brave) then the plugin has potential to be useful.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:112:\"Fully featured events calendar, booking registration (RSVP), recurring events, locations management, Google Maps\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/events-manager.6.5.2.zip\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";s:137:\"<p>For those upgrading from version 4 to 5, please <a href=\"http://wp-events-plugin.com/updating-to-v5/\">read these instructions</a>.</p>\";}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:18:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2760880\";s:7:\"caption\";s:130:\"Innovative responsive calendar with rings to show eventful dates, colored by category, clickable to expand more event information.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=2760880\";s:7:\"caption\";s:60:\"Completely customizable event widgets/blocks and shortcodes.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=2760880\";s:7:\"caption\";s:79:\"Beautiful event pages which can be completely customized via our settings page.\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=2760880\";s:7:\"caption\";s:46:\"Share your events to popular calendar clients.\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=2760880\";s:7:\"caption\";s:78:\"Display information about your location in widgets, blocks and shortcodes too.\";}i:6;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-6.png?rev=2844304\";s:7:\"caption\";s:121:\"Full-featured statistics and insights into your ticket sales via multiple graph types, including comparison and stacking.\";}i:7;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/events-manager/assets/screenshot-7.png?rev=2844304\";s:7:\"caption\";s:78:\"Easily skip to the future wit